description: Redevelopment of the site to provide 91 residential units (12 affordable and 79 market tenure, Class C3) in a building comprising basement, ground and four upper storeys, with basement parking (access via Maygrove Road) and associated hard & soft landscaping (following the demolition of office and residential buildings at 65 and 67 Maygrove Road).
